data.title: The Enchanted Forest
data.meta_description: The Enchanted Forest will return to Pitlochry in 2023. The ticket on sale NOW! Thursday 5th October 2023 – Sunday 5th November 2023

ENCHANTED FOREST REVEALS ITS FIRST EVER ANIMATED SHOW MAP

The Enchanted Forest, Scotland’s favourite sound and light show has revealed the event’s first ever animated show map. The event, which takes place between 3 October and 3 November 2024 in Pitlochry, Highland Perthshire, is a…
